{"tid":2082641,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"咪再帶美國旗同港獨旗出街，仲要定期清理手機，執生保命！","createTime":"2020-06-28T07:49:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-01T05:55:23.000Z","uid":219007,"like":24,"dislike":192,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"41c57159b05abc481e83d47ccca3e82d65695491","tid":2082641,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T07:49:03.000Z","msg":"以前有D野做完無乜代價，但今日已經唔同。今日早返嗰陣時嘅行為隨時坐三五七碌。<br />\n<br />\n唔係叫大家放棄，係希望大家執生保命。 唔通係《國安法》下係警察面前仲大叫港獨咁On9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n未來遊行一定會繼續出現大圍搜加捕<br />\n<br />\n若搜出有美國國旗、英國國旗、光復旗及港獨旗，係《國安法》下根本咬硬。 而且仲未知法律條文中警方有冇權去查人手機，如果有嘅話大家要更加小心，定期清理手機。<br />\n<br />\n口號係安全情況之下叫下冇所謂，但物件尤其是旗呢D，根本好難快速地Dup底，一搜到真係洗定囉柚都得。<br />\n為左執生自保，唔好帶多餘嘅嘢去街<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所有要做既野，唔該要係安全情況之下先好做<br />\n<br />\n執生保命之為重要！"},{"pid":"bf52c45dbdf1c7c848241e52ccb3fb0cfd2df4e6","tid":2082641,"uid":143343,"like":61,"dislike":10,"score":51,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T07:50:14.000Z","msg":"咁洗唔洗帶支那旗出街<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母"},{"pid":"a0ab4d8f79f1e2c31af07966e03825ec40c2161a","tid":2082641,"uid":303304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T07:51:26.000Z","msg":"［71前夕重開求幫推］全民報哨<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2082558\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2082558</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f862582b0dc71b74d4011113497aa646e8785092","tid":2082641,"uid":191812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T07:51:58.000Z","msg":"美國衫"},{"pid":"115486fff4137413fd37f21ca8e10e84741c4287","tid":2082641,"uid":222970,"like":42,"dislike":3,"score":39,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T07:52:39.000Z","msg":"有國旗都會拉 咁好多牌子嘅T恤 着出街都賴嘢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bjQfxsb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbjQfxsb.jpg&h=ad609486&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"175b7203ba69a85608a38e98aa51dc676ab0709a","tid":2082641,"uid":219007,"like":27,"dislike":17,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T07:54:40.000Z","msg":"連登仔班小學雞一定分唔到「執生」同「放棄」<br />\n<br />\n跟住話我叫人放棄，所以係五毛<br />\n<br />\n《國安法》通過咗之後，美國旗仲大鑊過有裝<br />\n<br />\n咁而家大家平時都習慣執生，唔係下下都帶裝出街<br />\n<br />\n咁唔一定下下帶支代價咁大既旗<br />\n<br />\n做任何行動包括抗爭正常都會係安全情況之下先做（唔想俾人捉）好正常<br />\n<br />\n係明知會俾人咬嘅情況之下，試問大家仲會唔會喺狗面前大叫港獨？？ <br />\n<br />\n呢啲叫執生保命，留低有用之驅，而唔係叫做放棄<br />\n<br />\n做嘢代價越來越大，大家要小心行事"},{"pid":"67b70fdb2a8fedf88016a8684b6b805a6a19c367","tid":2082641,"uid":112581,"like":29,"dislike":5,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T07:56:34.000Z","msg":"係人都知國安法係莫須有罪名<br />\n要咬你唔需要證據<br />\n點解仲要自己閹自己？"},{"pid":"da61cd2c8042050192bcfb9072b5c1a3bd23af15","tid":2082641,"uid":219007,"like":10,"dislike":3,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"115486fff4137413fd37f21ca8e10e84741c4287","tid":2082641,"uid":222970,"like":42,"dislike":3,"score":39,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T07:52:39.000Z","msg":"有國旗都會拉 咁好多牌子嘅T恤 着出街都賴嘢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bjQfxsb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbjQfxsb.jpg&h=ad609486&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T07:57:43.000Z","msg":"再同佢嘈呢啲嘢冇用㗎啦<br />\n<br />\n而家擺明根據政治立場拉人<br />\n<br />\n你仲同佢嘈呢啲嘢係因為你根據普通法習慣去諗<br />\n<br />\n但而家佢係唔會再根據呢啲嘢黎行事<br />\n<br />\n普通人着呢啲衫一定唔會拉<br />\n<br />\n但你身上有支大美國旗，而又係遊行地區附近搜到，咁係人都知你想點啦。 咁咪咬得lor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1f21d5afb3036803e1c173a6b1e0da27562cf84","tid":2082641,"uid":17866,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T07:58:25.000Z","msg":"周街都米字旗同美國旗衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />全部拉曬未"},{"pid":"c4b292b741a67b873cbbe42a3efb9c1bdca2684c","tid":2082641,"uid":24160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T07:58:58.000Z","msg":"咁不如遊行都唔好出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a17d4293328f252f289cab3517950649debfbad","tid":2082641,"uid":280475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T07:59:08.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"d6620b4aff9b230073662499b78fd03541d97844","tid":2082641,"uid":36995,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"67b70fdb2a8fedf88016a8684b6b805a6a19c367","tid":2082641,"uid":112581,"like":29,"dislike":5,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T07:56:34.000Z","msg":"係人都知國安法係莫須有罪名<br />\n要咬你唔需要證據<br />\n點解仲要自己閹自己？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T07:59:50.000Z","msg":"兩種睇法都岩<br />\n自由唔應該放棄<br />\n但帶左就會做炮灰<br />\n<br />\n自問唔驚 有大把錢打官司<br />\n或者爛命一條 <br />\n可以幫手試共匪底線"},{"pid":"d55ff7e57cdffea11550a67d36b0bc0c64988f90","tid":2082641,"uid":12757,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T08:00:03.000Z","msg":"樓豬正垃圾<br />\n旗都無旗支 點叫英美繼續撐你啊<br />\n你出黎去行街啊？<br />\n影相影到 都唔撚知你支持定反對<br />\n咁你上街既定義係咩"},{"pid":"96dd49958dafefc3bda247f1d923e12f4a9dba98","tid":2082641,"uid":219007,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d6620b4aff9b230073662499b78fd03541d97844","tid":2082641,"uid":36995,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"67b70fdb2a8fedf88016a8684b6b805a6a19c367","tid":2082641,"uid":112581,"like":29,"dislike":5,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T07:56:34.000Z","msg":"係人都知國安法係莫須有罪名<br />\n要咬你唔需要證據<br />\n點解仲要自己閹自己？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T07:59:50.000Z","msg":"兩種睇法都岩<br />\n自由唔應該放棄<br />\n但帶左就會做炮灰<br />\n<br />\n自問唔驚 有大把錢打官司<br />\n或者爛命一條 <br />\n可以幫手試共匪底線"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T08:01:42.000Z","msg":"岩啦，你呢個講法最公道<br />\n<br />\n自己衡量自己負得起代價嘅程度<br />\n<br 